---
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>You're on the list. Here's what's next. — Acorn</title>
<meta name="description" content="You're on the Acorn waitlist. Watch the briefing and book your call." />
<meta name="robots" content="noindex" />

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=EB+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

<style>
  :root {
    --surface: #fbf9f8;
    --surface-container-lowest: #ffffff;
    --surface-container-low: #f6f3f2;
    --surface-container: #f0eded;
    --surface-container-high: #eae8e7;
    --on-surface: #1b1c1c;
    --on-surface-variant: #404945;
    --outline: #717974;
    --outline-variant: #c0c8c3;
    --primary: #00261b;
    --on-primary: #ffffff;
    --primary-container: #0a3d2f;
    --on-primary-container: #79a896;
    --inverse-primary: #a0d1bd;
    --secondary: #006a62;
    --tertiary: #2a1d17;
    --background: #fbf9f8;

    --font-serif: 'EB Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    --font-sans: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, sans-serif;

    --radius: 0.25rem;
    --radius-md: 0.375rem;
    --radius-lg: 0.5rem;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    background: var(--background);
    color: var(--on-surface);
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
  }

  .display-lg {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5.5vw, 56px);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
  }
  .headline-xl {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 40px);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .label-sm {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav.topbar {
    padding: 20px 40px;
    background: var(--background);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--outline-variant);
  }
  .nav-inner {
    max-width: 1240px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .brand {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--primary-container);
  }
  .brand svg { width: 22px; height: 22px; }
  .brand-text {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--primary-container);
  }
  .nav-back {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .nav-back:hover { color: var(--primary-container); }

  /* CONFIRMATION */
  .confirmation {
    padding: 80px 40px 60px;
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--background);
  }
  .confirmation-inner {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .checkmark {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--primary-container);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    color: var(--primary-container);
  }
  .checkmark svg { width: 24px; height: 24px; }
  .confirmation .eyebrow { color: var(--primary-container); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .confirmation h1 { margin-bottom: 22px; color: var(--on-surface); }
  .confirmation .lead {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* SECTION */
  .section {
    padding: 64px 40px;
    background: var(--surface-container-low);
  }
  .section-inner {
    max-width: 980px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .card {
    background: var(--surface-container-lowest);
    border: 1px solid var(--outline-variant);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 36px;
  }
  .card .label-sm { margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .card h2 { margin-bottom: 18px; color: var(--on-surface); }
  .card p {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  /* VIDEO PLACEHOLDER (dark) */
  .video-card {
    margin-top: 26px;
    background: var(--primary-container);
    color: var(--on-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 48px 36px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .video-card .vc-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--inverse-primary);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .video-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--on-primary);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .video-card p {
    color: var(--on-primary-container);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 480px;
  }

  /* EXPECTATIONS */
  .exp-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 18px 0 0;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .exp-list li {
    padding: 16px 20px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    background: var(--surface-container);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--on-surface);
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .exp-list li::before {
    content: "";
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--primary-container);
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-top: 8px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* CALENDLY */
  .calendly-section {
    background: var(--primary);
    color: var(--on-primary);
    padding: 72px 40px 80px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .calendly-section .label-sm {
    color: var(--inverse-primary);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .calendly-section h2 {
    color: var(--on-primary);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .calendly-section .sub {
    color: var(--on-primary-container);
    font-size: 16px;
    margin: 0 auto 36px;
    max-width: 520px;
  }
  .calendly-inline-widget {
    background: var(--surface-container-lowest);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    max-width: 980px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer.footer {
    padding: 32px 40px;
    background: var(--background);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--outline-variant);
  }
  .footer-inner {
    max-width: 1240px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .footer-meta {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 22px; }
  .footer-links a {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--primary-container); }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    nav.topbar { padding: 14px 20px; }
    .confirmation { padding: 56px 20px 40px; }
    .section { padding: 48px 20px; }
    .card { padding: 28px; }
    .video-card { padding: 36px 24px; }
    .calendly-section { padding: 56px 20px 64px; }
    footer.footer { padding: 24px 20px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="topbar">
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="/" class="brand">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <path d="M12 2C9 5 7 8 7 12c0 3.5 2 6 5 7 3-1 5-3.5 5-7 0-4-2-7-5-10z" fill="currentColor"/>
        <path d="M12 9v13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      </svg>
      <span class="brand-text">Acorn</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/" class="nav-back">← Back to home</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="confirmation">
  <div class="confirmation-inner">
    <div class="checkmark">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M5 12l5 5L20 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div class="label-sm eyebrow">You're on the waitlist</div>
    <h1 class="display-lg">You're in. Here's what's next.</h1>
    <p class="lead">Watch the briefing, then book a call. We'll figure out the fit together. I'm only taking founders most likely to push the system to greatness, and this conversation is how I learn whether that's you.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="label-sm">Step one</div>
      <h2 class="headline-xl">Watch the briefing first.</h2>
      <p>A short video walking you through what Acorn is, who it's for, and what we'll cover on the call. Five minutes. Worth watching before you book.</p>

      <div class="video-card">
        <div class="vc-eyebrow">Coming soon</div>
        <h3>Briefing video</h3>
        <p>The briefing video is being recorded this week. For now, book a call below and I'll walk you through it live.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" style="background: var(--surface-container);">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="label-sm">Step two</div>
      <h2 class="headline-xl">What to expect on the call.</h2>
      <ul class="exp-list">
        <li>30 minutes. No pitch. We talk about what you're trying to build and where AI is helping or breaking.</li>
        <li>I'll ask about your team size, current AI use, and what sovereignty means in your context.</li>
        <li>If Acorn is a fit, you'll know on the call. If it's not, I'll tell you what would actually help.</li>
        <li>Bring your LinkedIn and your work email. The booking form will ask for both.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="calendly-section">
  <span class="label-sm">Book your orientation</span>
  <h2 class="headline-xl">Pick a time.</h2>
  <p class="sub">30 minutes. We'll figure out the fit together.</p>

  <!-- Calendly inline widget begin -->
  <div class="calendly-inline-widget" data-url="https://calendly.com/redbeardbrian/acorn-welcome?hide_event_type_details=1&hide_gdpr_banner=1&primary_color=0a3d2f" style="min-width:320px;height:720px;"></div>
<script is:inline type="text/javascript" src="https://assets.calendly.com/assets/external/widget.js" async></script>
  <!-- Calendly inline widget end -->
</section>

<footer class="footer">
  <div class="footer-inner">
    <a href="/" class="brand">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <path d="M12 2C9 5 7 8 7 12c0 3.5 2 6 5 7 3-1 5-3.5 5-7 0-4-2-7-5-10z" fill="currentColor"/>
        <path d="M12 9v13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      </svg>
      <span class="brand-text">Acorn</span>
    </a>
    <div class="footer-meta">&copy; 2026 Acorn Rooted Intelligence. Humans Orient. Agents Execute. Trust Is Earned.</div>
    <div class="footer-links">
      <a href="#">Privacy Protocol</a>
      <a href="#">Contact Concierge</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>